Personal Headline: CEO, COO, Board Member.
Description:
In the summer of 2021, the Danish Ministry of Defense published a broad political agreement that the Danish navy must be strengthened with a new multifunctional patrol ship type. While the Navy's current patrol ships carry out patrolling and monitoring of Danish waters and participate in rescue missions (SAR), the patrol ships of the future must be able to carry out more complex defense and environmental tasks. 

The new ship type is being developed to handle a wide range of complex military and civilian tasks and will future-proof the Navy's ability to defend and secure Danish waters. Danske Patruljeskibe K/S is a consortium formed by OMT Naval ApS, Terma and PensionDanmark. 

The purpose of the consortium is to offer itself as a total supplier for the Swedish Navy's future multifunctional patrol ships. Through Danske Patruljeskibe, OMT's shipbuilding expertise and Terma's military skills are combined, while PensionDanmark provides the financial security. 

As a total supplier, Danske Patruljeskibe will shoulder the responsibility for designing an innovative and modular ship design, building the ships and securing the Navy's investment through careful maintenance of the new patrol ships.

Personal Headline: Blockchain Certified | Web 3.0, NFT & Metaverse Enthusiast | Marketing Expert | FinTech | Innovation
Description:
Welcome everyone, today I would like to introduce to you an exciting new decentralized finance (DeFi) project that aims to revolutionize the way we think about fundraising and distribution in the movie industry.

Our project, called "FilmFinance.app", is a blockchain-based platform that allows filmmakers and other content creators to raise funds for their movies, short films, and web-series through a variety of innovative financing mechanisms. This includes crowdfunding, tokenized investment opportunities, and even a "watch-to-earn" program where viewers can earn money by watching ads in between the films they watch.

FilmFinance.app is built on top of a decentralized blockchain infrastructure, which provides a number of key benefits for filmmakers and other content creators. For example, by using blockchain technology, we can create a secure and transparent digital rights management system that protects the intellectual property rights of filmmakers and other content creators.

In addition to fundraising, FilmFinance.app also provides a distribution platform for films, short films and web-series on our platform. Our distribution platform allows content creators to reach a wider audience and monetize their films through various models such as pay-per-view or subscription-based models.

But what sets FilmFinance.app apart is our "watch-to-earn" program. This program allows viewers to earn money by watching ads in between the films they want to watch, giving them an incentive to watch more films and support the content creators on our platform.

We believe that FilmFinance.app is an innovative new project that has the potential to disrupt the way the movie industry operates and opens up new opportunities for filmmakers and audiences alike. We invite you to join us on this journey and support independent filmmakers and content creators. Thank you for your time and attention.

Personal Headline: Make bureaucracy simple
Description:
Expats and refugees often face significant difficulties communicating with official institutions (immigration services, social services, banks, medical and educational institutions, etc.). One of the reasons for these types of difficulties is, in particular, the German law that most government and non-government institutions are required to communicate with residents through the â€œold but good" paper correspondence, in other words, by sending letters printed on paper and sent by mail (although electronic correspondence only slightly eases the life of recipients who do not speak the language of the receiving country). 

The main purpose of Ridocu as a company is to facilitate communication and correspondence management for expats and refugees who have, frequent communication with officials or other authorities whose language of communication is not the native one of the users. Moreover, even sufficient language speaking is not always a guarantee of full-fledged communication with the government or any other institutions mentioned above.

Ridocu offers a solution to a significant portion of these problems through a mobile application based on a unique, company-developed, GPT-based Artificial Intelligence technology, allowing users to photograph the letter or, in the case of electronic correspondence, simply upload a PDF, text, or other files; after processing the photo of the letter or uploaded file, the system will do the rest.

Sounds interesting? Contact us to get more information about the company and the product

Personal Headline: Founder at Stillie // Communications & marketing professional
Description:
Stillie is on a mission to make prenatal and postpartum lactation care more accurate and more accessible through digital innovation.

Although breast milk is the normative feeding for infants, breastfeeding rates around the globe are lower than recommended. In Germany, 90% of mothers desire to breastfeed, but only 68% breastfeed after birth and 13% till the recommended 6 months. The main reasons for early cessation of breastfeeding are perceived low milk supply and breast problems like mastitis, which all can be addressed with better breastfeeding support. With the Stillie app, we want to provide parents with better and more accessible lactation care. 

Low breastfeeding rates and early cessation of breastfeeding have significant negative health and social impacts on women, children, the community, and the environment, lead to increased spending on national health care, and increase health inequities. Protection, promotion, and support of breastfeeding is a public health priority around the world.

Personal Headline: Co-Founder, CPO GoElektrik
Description:
Wir elektrifizieren Deutschland!

Durch die Errichtung von Ladestationen in deutschen Haushalten beteiligt sich GoElektrik aktiv an der Energiewende fur die E-Mobilitat von morgen.
 
Unsere Teammitglieder kommen aus der Automobilindustrie, der E-Mobilitatsbranche und der Elektroindustrie und haben zusammen mehr als 25 Jahre Erfahrung in diesem Bereich.

Wir bieten alles aus einer Hand

Wir kennen die Herausforderung, die passende Wallbox auszuwahlen und einen Elektriker zu finden, der sie installiert.
Unsere Losung ubernimmt alles von der Planung, dem Kostenvoranschlag, der Installation, der Inbetriebnahme und den Formalitaten, alles aus einer Hand.

Wussten Sie, dass die meisten Ladezyklen zu Hause stattfinden?

80 % der Ladezyklen werden nicht uber die offentliche Infrastruktur abgewickelt. Bis 2030 wird in Deutschland ein Bedarf von 8,6 Millionen privater Ladepunkte geschatzt, das bedeutet, dass in den nachsten 7 Jahren taglich 5585 Ladestationen installiert werden!

Wir wollen Deutschland helfen, eine emissionsfreie Energie- und Mobilitatszukunft zu gestalten.

Unsere Losung: Dank unserer Software sind wir in der Lage, Privatkunden und Unternehmen, die eine Ladestation zu Hause installieren wollen, eine schnelle und bequeme Installation im "All-Inclusive-Paket" mit Beratung, Wallbox-Ladestationen und Installation aus einer Hand zu fairen und transparenten Kosten anzubieten.

Personal Headline: Senior Digital Marketing Manager at iVvy
Description:
Burleigh Chilli Co. came to life through two mates living the Gold Coast life, enjoying the sun, surf, and community vibes of Burleigh. As they sat at their local brewery having a yarn over a few pale ales, co-founders Justin and Sean knew they wanted to start a business together. They began to brainstorm ideas, and began work on a few that eventually fizzled out. During this time they found a passion for getting in the kitchen and experimenting with their favourite chillies, but never thought it could turn into anything more than that. 

After surprising their friends at a dinner party with an experimental hot sauce, they knew they were onto a winning formula, and Burleigh Chilli Co. was born.

The name Burleigh Chilli Co. came about through their love of the Burleigh lifestyle, and they knew they wanted to bring that sense of community into the flavours and branding of the product. 

Each of our core range of sauces are modelled after some common waves youâ€™ll see around the Burleigh headland. We start off with the Ankle Biter which provides the most mild of kicks, then comes the Point Break stepping up the heat, and finally the Cyclone Swell for the more adventurous chilli lover. None of our sauces are designed to blow your head off - we are all about adding flavour and fun to your meal, without destroying your taste buds like some other sauces only meant for chilli eating competitions.

Personal Headline: CEO Mint Watch - Business Development presso DeA Capital RE SGR - Master in Real Estate presso SDA Bocconi - Assistente ricercatore presso SDA Bocconi
Description:
About us:
We are a blockchain trading company of luxury watches; we are a team of experts with expertise ranging from quantitative finance, legal, to IT. 

Our mission:
To democratise investment in the management of luxury watches, in a historical context where liquidity management is a daunting challenge even for professional investors.

Our business model:
We are the first to leverage blockchain technology to enable exposure to the management of luxury watches, a performing, appealing, resilient and growing real asset: the ideal underlying asset for any mean-variance investor.

We fund ourselves through Security Token Offerings to buy watches, build portfolios, trade and distribute revenues.
The Security Tokens issued are high-yield debt securities: they give patrimonial rights to the subscribers. We reward the investor with a remuneration model free of accounting wizardry, recognising a revenue share: we do not parcel out asset ownership, we adopt a revenue sharing model. 

We adopt a hybrid, trading-value strategy: one part of the portfolio remains 'stationary', exploiting the tendency of references to appreciate, while the other is rotated. This generates a leverage effect that would otherwise be absent in a static model; the earnings that are recapitalised increase the AUM. The underlying is likened to an asset that pays out and recapitalises dividends.

Our approach is data-driven: we implement, develop and constantly update statistical models that capture and forecast macro trends, using strategic partners. In the same way we build portfolios, seeking effective and efficient allocations.

Reason why:
- Novelty, exclusivity and goodness of the asset
- Reference market characteristics
- Decorrelation to listed markets
- Emotional value of the object, a safe haven asset and an exceptional investment 
- The underlying is a physical security
- Through DLT we implicitly make the asset liquid and tradable
- Revenue sharing at 3/5 years.

The world is constantly evolving, and there is no better way to stay up to date on the latest advances and trends than by reading research articles. Whether it's in the fields of science, technology, business, social sciences, history, or any other area, research articles provide valuable insights and analysis on important topics.

A blog dedicated to research articles can be a great resource for anyone looking to learn more about a particular subject or stay current on the latest research in their field. With so much information available online, it can be difficult to know where to start when looking for quality research. A well-curated blog can help readers find the most relevant and interesting research articles, saving them time and effort.

In a research-based blog, readers can expect to find in-depth analysis and commentary on current research findings. The blog can cover a wide range of topics, from the latest scientific breakthroughs and technological innovations to important social and political issues. The articles can be written in a variety of styles, from informative and educational to thought-provoking and opinionated.

One of the benefits of a research-based blog is that it can help bridge the gap between academia and the wider public. Many research articles are written in highly technical language that can be difficult for non-experts to understand. A blog that translates this research into more accessible language can help make these important findings more accessible to a wider audience.

Whether you're a student, a professional, or just someone who's interested in learning more about the world around you, a research-based blog can be a valuable resource. By providing in-depth analysis and commentary on important research findings, such a blog can help you stay up to date on the latest advances and trends in your field, and keep you informed on important issues that affect us all.

Description:
Moodflik was developed based on the fact that regardless of who we are, where we are from or what we believe, we all share one commonality â€“ we all see, experience and react to things and events that we either love or dislike at any given moment in our lives; though we may sometimes go through these life experiences sub-consciously. We have also come to understand that most of the communications exchanged on many social media platforms can really be summarised into these two areas, thus filtering out irrelevant content.

It is our mission here at Moodflik to provide a fun, unique, engaging, diverse and safe platform for people from various walks of life with different values, opinions & perspectives to share their daily moments of joy & happiness as well as times of frustrations & dissatisfactions in the forms of likes & dislikes respectively and respectfully; whereby users can share 'like' posts represented in a green background & 'dislike' posts in red, for a user to easily decipher the context of a post.

We believe that sharing a balance of these two dichotomies of life provides a more comprehensive and candid overview of how we truly are both inwardly and outwardly, by expressing these constantly changing dual aspects of our daily reactions to lifeâ€™s events we can better understand how our Moods flik (sorry, couldnâ€™t resist :).

We have come a very long way to make this platform a reality despite the numerous obstacles and challenges that have come our way, we maintained a can-do and never-give-up attitude because we are confident that Moodflik will play a key role in shaping a new approach to dialogue and purposeful content sharing on social media. Currently (to our knowledge), there are no other social media platforms offering this form of micro-blogging, so we hope you enjoy this new and unique experience with us as we continue in our plans to grow bigger, better and bolder.

P.s Yes, we are aware that flik is not a word, but we are currently loving it ;)

Personal Headline: gridBPM CEO
Description:
gridBPM is a content technology and services company focused on helping Building Product Manufacturers (BPM) promote their brand and products to Architects, Engineers and Contractors practicing BIM in the commercial construction arena.  As BIM has evolved, BPMs have had to become more actively involved in the Sales & Marketing of their products to deliver the right data to get their products discovered and used in BIM projects.  While BPMs have typically invested in Revit BIM models, there remains further challenges to expand their digital footprint to serve more construction professionals, win more projects and drive a higher ROI from their content investments.

BIM and digitization have brought BPMs new opportunities along with a new set of marketing problems to be solved:

How to expand market reach and access a larger audience of design and construction professionals to generate more project opportunities.

How to create and deliver a growing library of high-quality BIM content cost effectively and within reasonable timelines â€“ especially with new product introductions.

How to keep content up-to-date not only on the corporate website but throughout the many web destinations users expect to discover BIM-ready products.

How to analyze and assess the effectiveness of these content syndication and brand awareness efforts to enhance and course-correct.

Ultimately, BPMs are looking to build brand awareness, get their products into more projects and be recognized by the design & construction community for delivering high quality BIM content and a top-notch digital customer experience.

BPMs must be market agnostic and participate in any and all AEC related content destinations to serve exiting customers and attract new ones.  gridBPM and its BIM Content Delivery Network (CDN) helps manufacturers publish their products to multiple web destinations while driving traffic back to their branded website.

Personal Headline: Founder & CEO of Flexibus
Industry: Transportation, Logistics, Supply Chain and Storage
Description:
Flexibus technology firm is revolutionizing everyday bus travel by offering innovative solutions such as live bus tracking, contactless payment systems, giving out the number of passengers and also the exact times of the end of the journey using in-house GPS trackers for not only smart busses but even the local busses.

Our App will connect to the existing smart busses to track and send live data which our algorithm will process according to the speed and traffic around the bus in order to calculate the exact time of the journey. The ringer feature automatically alerts you 5 mins before the bus arrives or before you end your journey. Using the sensors near the door we can give an exact count of the number of people on the bus so you will never have to worry about traveling uncomfortably. Using in-house built Gps and sensor tracking you can turn any normal or old bus into a smart Flexibus.

The Seamless UI/UX experience will deliver a quality experience to users while ensuring simplicity of use, making it accessible to users across all age groups.

These services aim to enhance the safety and reliability of bus travel, which is a basic necessity, akin to water and air. Despite a growing population of individuals who travel regularly, only a limited segment of the Indian population, approximately 15%, have access to private modes of transportation such as cars, taxis, or motorcycles. 

The remaining 85% rely solely on public transportation. However, with the increasing traffic congestion and its adverse effects, it has become evident that private transportation is creating more problems than it is resolving. A rising demographic is opting to forgo car and motorcycle ownership altogether.

Hence with Flexibus, no matter in which part of India you are traveling, bus transport will never be a hassle for travelers anymore.

Personal Headline: Deal Sourcing for Lower Mid-Market Cross-Border M&A
Description:
Orion Cross-Border Operations LLC (OCBO) specializes in providing deal sourcing for lower mid-market cross-border M&A, connecting North American Buyers to European Sellers. Our mission is to help our clients expand their business horizons and tap into the vast potential of the European market.

As the baby boomer generation in Europe retires and sells off their businesses, many small and medium-sized enterprises are becoming available for purchase. This presents a unique opportunity for American middle market companies to expand their global reach and gain a foothold in the European market. At OCBO, we can help our clients capitalize on this opportunity by connecting them with potential Sellers and facilitating cross-border M&A deals.

At OCBO, we believe that successful cross-border M&A requires not only financial expertise but also cultural and linguistic knowledge. We pride ourselves on our deep understanding of both the North American and European markets, as well as our ability to bridge the gap between the two.

When you work with OCBO, you also gain access to our trusted network of local partners in your target country that can provide legal, accounting, HR, tax, and other services during the due diligence process or post-acquisition integration phase. If you are looking for a full-service boutique investment bank in Europe instead, we can also provide a selection of the most relevant investment bankers with regards to your goals, industry, and strategy and carry out introductions.

At OCBO, we are dedicated to helping North American Buyers expand into Europe by providing personalized, comprehensive, and cost-effective M&A scouting services. Contact us today at n.graves@orioncbo.com to learn more about how we can help your company achieve its global growth goals.

Personal Headline: Indiepreneur & Freelance // Builder
Description:
Hey there! I'm Mael, the developper behind WhisperBot. Loads of people send voice messages. For me, 7 times out of 10, I'm in a situation where I can't listen to it directly : people around, no Airpods on, just too focused on my work to listen to a voice ... So many reasons can lead to that. How many times dit that happen to you ? 
That's why I decided to develop WhisperBot, and challenged myself with a 7-day challenge to create a product that could simplify WhatsApp communications for everyone. Well, it took actually 17 days, as I spent more time than expected on some parts and was travelling (moved from Koh Samui , to Bali , spending few days in Kuala Lumpur  on the way)
I believe that transparency and authenticity are the keys to building trust, which is why I've chosen to #buildinpublic. I regularly share updates on the development process, challenges I face, and successes I achieve on my personal Twitter account (@maelus_). If you're curious about my journey, want to exchange ideas, or just love tech as much as I do, feel free to follow me and join the conversation. 
With WhisperBot, my mission is to empower you with a tool that streamlines communication and makes voice message transcription as seamless as possible. First step is transcription. Some other features are coming up .
If you have any suggestions, feedback, or questions, please don't hesitate to reach out. I'm always eager to learn & grow - let's use collective intelligence's power to make WhisperBot the best it can be for you.
Hope you'll enjoy WhisperBot's use

Personal Headline: CEO and Founder at Beautiful Minds ABA PLLC.
Description:
Our Approach: Because kids are kids only one time in their life. ABA has to be FUN!!!
At Beautiful Minds we focused on Naturalistic Teaching Methods. 
Each one of our staff and parents are presented with the components of Pivotal Response Training. 

Pivotal Response Treatment, or PRT, is a behavioral treatment for autism. This therapy is play-based and initiated by the child. PRT is based on the principles of Applied Behavior Analysis (ABA).

Goals of this approach include:
*  Development of communication and language skills
*  Increasing positive social behaviors
*  Relief from disruptive self-stimulatory behaviors

The PRT therapist targets â€œpivotalâ€� areas of a childâ€™s development instead of working on one specific behavior. By focusing on pivotal areas, PRT produces improvements across other areas of social skills, communication, behavior and learning.

Pivotal areas include: 
* Motivation
* Response to multiple cues
*  Self-management 
* Initiation of social interactions 

Motivation strategies are an important part of the PRT approach. These emphasize
natural reinforcement. For example, if a child makes a meaningful attempt to request a stuffed animal, the reward is the stuffed animal â€“ not a candy or other unrelated reward. Children are rewarded for making a good attempt, even if it is not perfect.

Personal Headline: Specialist in Water Management | Micro-irrigation | Climate action | Artificial glaciers | Renewable energy | Agri-business | Sustainability
Description:
Our mission is to promote holistic water management in mountain regions by offering a range of climate-resilient solutions, including ice stupas, ice terraces, glacial covers, snow harvesting, glacial lake management, and more.

Glaciers in mountain regions around the world are melting at an alarming rate, which poses a serious threat to the communities that rely on them for water. In the Himalayas, for example, melting glaciers are leading to erratic and unpredictable water supplies, which makes it difficult for farmers to plan their crops and for communities to access clean drinking water.

At Acres of Ice, we offer a range of solutions to address these challenges. In addition to building ice stupas, ice terraces, and other innovative ice reservoirs, we work with mountain communities to develop holistic water management plans that include glacial covers, snow harvesting, and glacial lake management. We value the wisdom of these communities and believe that their input is critical to creating sustainable, long-term solutions.

As a company, we are committed to driving climate action and raising awareness about the consequences of climate change. We believe that nature-based solutions like the ones we offer at Acres of Ice can help build resilience in mountain communities and contribute to a more sustainable future for all.

Personal Headline: Manager for British International Investment Development Impact Evaluations team & Technical Director of the Joint Impact Model
Description:
The Joint Impact Model Foundation was established in 2022 to create credible oversight of the Joint Impact Model (JIM) and its development.

Characterized by its harmonized and transparent methodology, the JIM is a model which enables the quantification of indirect jobs, value added, and greenhouse gas (GHG) emissions related to investments of financial institutions. The aim of the JIM is to bring comparability, accountability, and transparency to the financial industry.

Using input data such as revenue and power production from investment portfolios, the JIM enables users to estimate financial flows through the economy and its resulting economic (value added), social (employment) and environmental (greenhouse gas emissions) impact. These impacts can be used to measure and report on the contribution of individual institutions to the Paris Agreement and the UN Sustainable Development Goals.

The JIM is a crucial tool in the efforts against climate change, since measuring and reporting on impact in a consistent and comparable way is essential to evaluate progress towards global development needs and priorities, assess effectiveness of investments and drive impactful actions.

You are already involved in driving the Mental Health & Wellbeing initiative in your workplace, formally or as a volunteer. And while you know you are always doing your best, you wonderâ€¦ how is it met by others?

Teodora, our founder,  spent the last two years setting up and driving the mental health & wellbeing initiative for her former workplace, Amazon Fashion in Europe.

Personal Headline: Director at Tin | Founder at Tina | Exploring the roots of toxic workplace culture and offering support to those affected
Description:
For over two decades, Silicon Valley has been the epicentre of a business philosophy that worships at the altar of over-evaluations and treats "moving fast and breaking things" as its holy doctrine. This mindset has eroded workers' rights and stability, not just at the start-ups in San Francisco, but around the world at an alarming rate.

Mythologising a "fake it till you make it" mentality has given rise to an explosion of unqualified leaders. This approach, once hailed as the epitome of entrepreneurial spirit, has fostered a culture where deceit and arrogance are rewarded over genuine expertise and ethical conduct. In many instances, these so-called leaders rely on bullying tactics and manipulation to maintain their positions, further perpetuating a vicious cycle of toxicity and incompetence. 

Only by holding companies accountable for the toll that workplace abuse has on the workforce (not to mention their own financial bottom line), can we create lasting transformation. We will no longer tolerate being pushed to our breaking point and then cast aside like broken tools. Now is the moment to boldly speak truth to power, to make our voices heard and demand the respect we deserve. Together, we can forge a new, fairer future for all!

Personal Headline: Founder, Alco Therapeutics
Description:
Alco Therapeutics is a virtual pharmaceutical company dedicated to developing innovative treatments for neurobehavioral disorders, including Obsessive-Compulsive Disorder (OCD), Tourette's Syndrome, and Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis (ALS), by repurposing an existing, safe drug through our patent-pending treatment method.

Problem:
The current standard of care for OCD is limited by low efficacy and costly side effects, which leads a high percentage of patients to go untreated. As a result, patients face a high burden of disease and significantly diminished quality of life, creating an urgent demand for better therapeutic options. There have been no new approved treatments for OCD in more than twenty years.

Solution:
Alco Therapeutics is developing a proprietary treatment method based on histamine signaling pathways. Our approach has the potential to reduce OCD symptoms, enhancing the quality of life of patients and increasing their productivity and reducing comorbidities, disability and suicide rates. Due to positive anecdotal evidence and promising previous preclinical trial data, we believe our treatment can revolutionize the management of OCD and significantly improve patient outcomes.

Personal Headline: Senior Industrial Designer presso e-Novia
Description:
Laboris Catrame was born on a small plateau a few kilometers from the Royal Palace of Caserta. A handkerchief of land overlooking the Matese Massif and Mount Taburno, mountains that separate Upper Campania from Molise and Sannio Beneventano. The ancient volcano of Roccamonfina to the northwest and Vesuvius to the southeast place us in the middle of a vast amphitheater facing the sea which contains breathtaking landscapes and a particular microclimate.

A large area once called Terra Laboris.

A unique territory with great biodiversity that hosts the most important watercourses of Campania, the Volturno, and, the Calore Irpino which right at the foot of our plateau gives way to the other to converge towards the sea.
Terra Laboris is our history, our present and our future. It becomes the personification of our desire to tell it. Laboris is a member of the Tar family.

The intent is to rediscover the past in sustainability, balance and harmony with the elements of the earth.

The authenticity of a land returns unique and original wines.

With absolute attention to detail we translate the originality of the territory into wines of the highest quality.

Our wines are the maximum expression of two ancient recovered vineyards and of two native varieties of Alta Campania, Pallagrello Bianco and Casavecchia.

Personal Headline: Co-Founder of Dymium
Description:
Our mission is to establish the new standard method for the extraction of kidney stones. 

The current therapy options are based on the fragmentation of the stones. In this process, all resulting fragments must be located and extracted individually. Fragments left behind can lead to renewed stone growth, infections, and colic. It is assumed that approximately 50% of the patients have to be treated again due to these residues.

We have developed an innovative method for minimally invasive, magnetic removal of kidney stone fragments.

Description:
Hemora is a cutting-edge telemedicine application  that aims to make medical care more accessible to patients suffering from blood disorders. According to the World Health Organization, blood disorders affect at least 1 billion of the global population, and at least 1.25 million die from them yearly. Aside from anaemia, the most common blood disorder, sickle cell anaemia and thalassemia are the second most common blood disorders, affecting 400 million people globally. Hemora's goal is to provide patients suffering from any blood disorder with quality and consistent remote medical care in order for them to live longer and achieve their objectives.

Hemora intends to accomplish this through the Hemora mobile app, where doctors, specialists(doctors with more years of experience), nurses, nutritionists, and consultants specialising in haematology will treat patients with blood disorders from the comfort of their own homes. Hemora intends to collaborate with foundations, pharmacies, clinics, and hospitals.

Additional features for patients will be News and  Remote job availability from different companies. This is to help our patients integrate into society and improve their social well-being. 

if you are interested in investing in Hemora please do not hesitate to send us a mail at info@hemora.co

Personal Headline: making the world a better place
Description:
Imago provides gender-affirming hormone therapy (GAHT) available online and issues EU-valid prescriptions. Imago is founded on the principles of (1) respecting human rights and dignity of our patients, (2) being fully based on contemporary scientific knowledge, and (3) granting life-saving treatment in 4 hours, not 4 years.

67% of transitioning people think about suicide on regular basis before the hormonal transition and only 3% after receiving hormones. GAHT saves lives on a massive scale. It also saves from nightmares of depression and despair. The great majority of 6-11mln trans & non-binary individuals in the EU are instead sentenced to years (!) of depression and anguish by public healthcare systems, reducing their lifespan, often significantly. Furthermore, humiliating, pseudo-scientific and human-rights-violating procedures increase the already enormously high death toll in suicides. NGOs, scientists, and human rights advocates' pleas remain unanswered.

Imago operates in the Informed Consent Model (ICM), the detailed guidelines set developed based on the results of consistent and numerous current scientific research.

Inner Reconnection naar het Nederlands vertaald betekent letterlijk 'innerlijke herverbinding'. En dat is precies de missie van deze onderneming: zoveel mogelijk mensen helpen hun innerlijke verbinding weer te herstellen. 

Wanneer je leeft in verbinding met jezelf zit je in een positieve flow. Alles lijkt vanzelf te gaan, dingen die je nodig hebt verschijnen op een magische wijze op je pad en je zit vol energie. Wat anderen van je vinden bepaalt niet (langer) jouw leven - jij leeft op je eigen voorwaarden.

Een probleem los je niet op waar het is ontstaan, daarom organiseert Inner Reconnection retraites om even uit je dagelijkse omgeving te stappen. Tijdens deze retraites kan je ontdekken wie je diep van binnen echt bent, wat jouw dromen zijn in dit leven en wat je kan doen om deze te realiseren. Je mag helemaal jezelf zijn. Dat kan ook in de veilige setting. Met een kleine groep vrouwen ga je deze innerlijke reis aan. Je werkt aan je persoonlijke groei en er is tijd voor ontspanning & plezier. Je gaat naar huis met de nodige tools om zo ook na de retraite door te gaan met je waardevolle transformatie. Ga je mee op reis?

Description:
CloudForge: The premier workflow automation and data insights software, tailor-made for Metal Service Centers (MSCs) â€“ the backbone of America's industrial economy.

Metal Service Centers hold a pivotal position in the metal supply chain, processing and distributing half of the 88MM tons of steel produced in the US annually. Essential industries depend on MSCs for everything from aircraft and skyscrapers to HVAC units and medical devices.

Yet, despite their critical role, MSCs are held back by a software market dominated by outdated legacy solutions from the '70s and '80s, costing the $220B industry over $10B in unrealized earnings.

Personal Headline: Founder & Chief Evangelist at SmartEdgeAi
Description:
AI edge solutions refer to the application of artificial intelligence (AI) technology in edge computing. Edge computing refers to the practice of processing data at the "edge" of a network, closer to where the data is generated, rather than sending it to a centralized server or data center for processing.

AI edge solutions can provide several benefits, such as faster data processing, reduced latency, improved data privacy and security, and increased efficiency in data management. Personal Headline: Founder at Monapp
Description:
Monapp is a Nigerian financial technology startup that focuses on developing fast and secure payment solutions for the Nigerian market. The company's mission is to promote financial inclusion and reduce the reliance on cash transactions by providing a fast and efficient payment solution that can replace the overwhelming dependency on cash. Monapp utilizes QR code and blockchain technology to facilitate fast and secure payments, which can provide a seamless and contactless payment experience for users, while offering increased security and transparency.

As a Nigerian company targeting the local market, Monapp is well-positioned to understand the unique challenges and opportunities in the Nigerian financial sector. By leveraging the latest technologies and providing user-friendly solutions, Monapp can help to drive financial inclusion and improve access to financial services for individuals and businesses across the country.


Monapp's mobile application offers features such as expense tracking, budgeting, and the ability to connect bank accounts and credit cards. The app's security features include encryption and two-factor authentication, which are important for a financial management app.

Overall, Monapp is focused on leveraging technology to provide innovative solutions that can help to transform the financial landscape in Nigeria. The company's mission to promote financial inclusion and reduce the reliance on cash transactions is an important one, and has the potential to provide significant benefits to consumers, businesses, and the broader economy. With the increasing adoption of digital payments and the growing popularity of mobile banking in Nigeria, Monapp has a significant opportunity to provide innovative solutions that meet the needs of consumers and businesses in the region.

Personal Headline: Product Legal Lead @Omnipresent
Description:
At Tggl, we provide a feature flag service for agile teams to control the release process and manage feature flags across multiple platforms. Our interface allows your entire team to change what features are active on your app at any given time, without the need for lengthy deployment cycles or technical knowledge.

Our mission is to help teams move fast and safely release new features to their users. We created Tggl to simplify the release process for agile teams. Our powerful and flexible users segmentation allows you to manage release dates, enable features for specific users or countries, conduct A/B tests, and gradually release the feature to a percentage of your users until you reach 100%.

We value simplicity, performance, and resilience. We believe that feature flagging should be easy and accessible to everyone, not just developers.

What makes Tggl different is our user-friendly interface and powerful feature set. Unlike other providers, Tggl makes a minimal number of HTTP requests and the payload is always tiny. Our architecture is optimized to deliver flags evaluation as fast as possible, with a response time of less than 14ms. And because Tggl is resilient by design, your app will never crash because of feature flags and will always fall back to a safe state in case of service disruption, network error, or misconfiguration.

Control your release process with ease: With Tggl, you can manage feature flags across mobile, web, and even backend applications. Neatly organize your flags into projects and development environments. Conduct A/B tests, test in production with a few users, and progressively roll out to everyone risk-free.

If you're looking for a feature flag service that is built for performance and scale, try Tggl. Our architecture can scale endlessly to match your needs, and our platform is easy to use. Sign up today and start releasing your features with confidence!

Welcome to Blook, your ultimate travel partner. Our mission is to provide seamless travel experiences to our customers.

Our Services:

Our team is equipped to come alongside a film for the duration of the project to support the well-being of each individual both spiritually and physically. By listening, praying, encouraging, teaching, and serving, we influence the productions that are influencing culture.

We provide:
Spiritual Leadership - on the set, every day, until the last cast/crew member leaves for the day.
Wise Counsel - as needs arise (professional and/or personal), and we work to infuse a comprehensive biblical worldview into conversations.
Servant Leadership - by serving the cast/crew and being available to senior leadership for nearly any task, from conflict resolution to grilling hot dogs, etc.
Love & Compassion - as we develop authentic relationships with cast and crew and make ourselves "available" during the entire production phase.
Prayer Support - through a prayer team that covers the cast, crew, and set in prayer every day.
Worship & Devotions - woven into set life: 5-7 minute devotions held at the start of the day and weekly worship services that include music and a relevant message.

Foundational in everything Set Shepherds provides is a commitment to serve the producer/director in any way he/she deems necessary, to serve the cast and crew in a manner driven by the producer/director, and to ensure the team achieves their greatest potential.

Ultimately, our vision is to transform American culture by swimming upstream and affecting the culture on film sets - one "sheep at a time" (Luke 15:3-7).

Personal Headline: Co-Founder & CTO at Liquidium (Fungus Inc.). Leading Ordinal lending with Liquidium's innovative solutions. Dedicated to improving finance.
Description: Liquidium is a peer-to-peer lending solution that leverages the power of Discreet Log Contracts (DLCs) and Partially Signed Bitcoin Transactions (PSBTs) to enable users to borrow and lend native Bitcoin against native Ordinals as collateral. Ordinal Inscriptions are a new form of digital assets created by inscribing data on satoshis, the smallest unit of Bitcoin. Liquidium allows Ordinal owners to lock inscriptions as collateral to borrow Bitcoin, while retaining ownership and exposure to their Ordinal. The platform operates solely on the Bitcoin blockchain in a trust-minimal and custodian-free solution. The lending process is facilitated through PSBTs, and the loan outcomes are validated by DeepLake oracles. Liquidium is the biggest Bitcoin NFT lending protocol by volume on the Stacks blockchain for users to borrow against their Bitcoin NFTs.

Introducing the Kids News app, an exciting way for children to stay informed and engaged with the world around them. With each article they read, kids can earn coins that can be redeemed for vouchers and real cash.

Overall, the Kids News app is an innovative and engaging way for kids to stay informed about the world while also earning rewards for their efforts. Whether they're reading about the latest news or exploring a new topic, kids will love using this app and earning coins that they can redeem for real-world rewards.

Personal Headline: I Teach People How To Slow The Progression of Kidney Disease || Ready to Become Your Own Kidney Advocate?
Person Location: Santa Rosa Beach, Florida, United States
Description:
Optimal Kidney Health was founded by Julie Spears in 2023. After having a kidney removed in 2002 and receiving little guidance on how to manage and slow the progression of CKD, she decided to do something about it. 

Julie's journey to forming healthier habits led her to become an educator and advocate for kidney patients at DaVita, the largest provider of kidney care services in the U.S.

During her 17-year career at DaVita, Julie led a team of educators that delivered kidney disease education to more than 8,000 patients.

Today Julie a Certified Kidney Health Coach and founder of Optimal Kidney Health. She teaches people how to slow the progression of their kidney disease through simple and sustainable lifestyle changes. She also uses what she has learned from living daily with trauma and grief to help people love their life again.

Description:
A Shop My Feed chegou pra defender a autenticidade e a liberdade dos influenciadores, revolucionando a forma como seus seguidores interagem e compram produtos.

Por meio de um link in bio, seus seguidores tem acesso a uma copia do seu feed, com a diferenca que, em cada foto, eles tem acesso a links que redirecionam para a pagina de venda dos produtos presentes naquela foto. Assim que um seguidor realiza uma compra, voce ganha comissao. Dessa forma, voce pode focar apenas na producao do seu conteudo, mantendo a organicidade do seu perfil: Just... be yourself.

Para as marcas, elas poderao vender seus produtos de uma forma criativa, com um ROI mais alto comparado a outros canais, sem a necessidade de incorrer muito risco (dado o pagamento por performance).

Nosso SaaS transforma qualquer feed do Instagram em uma "loja", o seu shopping pessoal, democratizando o acesso a parcerias e oferecendo a qualquer creator a oportunidade de monetizar seu conteudo de forma pratica, rapida e facil.

Venha fazer parte dessa revolucao!

Personal Headline: Biologics and Cell Therapy Operations Start-Up, Scale-Up and Optimization
Description:
Use our toolkit to start and scale the right way so that your operations are safe, compliant and on schedule.

We all want safe and compliant GMP Manufacturing that starts on time, ends on time, is deviation free and has complete and accurate documentation.

However, the need to start up, scale up, or transform will always disrupt the steady state.  These changes increases the risk that something can and will go wrong.

These risks come in three areas:

Business Risk:  
Business risks  can Include delays, rework, deviations, lost batches, backlogs, regulatory compliance problems, and even in a worst case the loss of your company's right to operate.

Employee Risk:
Change fatigue can impact employee morale.  The constant need to "build the airplane while flying it" can be exhausting to employees,  people can become overwhelmed, and this can lead to burn out and attrition.

Compliance and Patient Risk:
Starting up and scaling up should never compromise quality.  Your patients depend on good manufacturing and patient safety should never be compromised during times of change and transformation.

Let GMPKit be your guide:

Personal Headline: Certified Coach & Co-Founder Rudder| Coaching, Training, Workshops| I help healthcare leaders increase engagement, build work/life balance, and increase confidence to create stronger leaders & better healthcare.
Description:
Are you a healthcare leader who is burnt-out, jaded, disconnected from your team, or unsure how to navigate the next few months (or few years)?

You're not alone.

Most of us entered healthcare because we wanted to help patients. As our careers grew, our roles changed:

- Some of us were promoted "up the chain" from floor nurse to charge, or from unit supervisor to director
- Some of us branched out on our own, starting individual practices
- Some of us were the "next person up" as people left the profession during the pandemic, being thrust into leadership positions on an interim or permanent basis (positions we maybe didn't want!)

While most of us completed years of schooling to care for our patients, few of us received training to handle the demands and challenges of leading in a healthcare environment. 

What became important to us changed. The focus went from caring for individual patients, to caring for colleagues, teams, organizations, business and financial goals, and so much more.

Many healthcare leaders struggle with this transition. 

That's why we founded Rudder.

We found that by providing individual and group coaching, training, workshops, and sharing the latest healthcare management research we could transform healthcare supervisors and practice founders into confident, balanced, healthy, and effective leaders.

The kind of leaders that teams look up to and want to follow.

The kind of leaders that have ambitious professional goals AND have robust and fulfilling personal lives. 

The kind of leaders who know where they are going, how they are going to get there, and how to care for their teams and organizations along the way.

We know our method works because it worked for our cofounder, and its worked for dozens of healthcare leaders who've taken the journey with us.

We invite you to invest 30 minutes with us by clicking the link below. We'll explore your challenges, goals, and discuss how Rudder can help you Navigate Your Life.

Description:
We spend 50%+ of our awake time working. Ideally, that provides us: a playground for self-realisation, engagement and connection, stimulus for growth, fun.

Not the case? Might be time for a change. 
Need help? click â†ªï¸� Contact us at the top.

I know first hand how scary, stressful and uncomfortable change can be.  Ask me how many times I have moved to a new city, or country, changed job, industry (or returned single!)

It took me a long time to understand what I like, what I need, what I want, what I deserve in my awake time. At work and beyond. 

Sometimes, to achieve that ideal we need CHANGE. It's the gateway to growth, discovery, it can bring perspective, surprises, opportunities and rewards. The key is to pursue ALIGNMENT.

With the Ride the Change alignment programmes I encourage people to listen to themselves to find their path. I believe that, deep down, you know what's best for you, and -with a supporting environment, guidance and time- you can find the answers yourself.

The outside "noise" can get in the way, and it's hard to hear that inner voice. 
It really makes a difference to have someone on your side who cares about you and your success, to help get back that clarity and move forward with confidence. 

My mission is be that person, and help you: 
* Notice, understand and overcome the fears and limiting beliefs that hold you back, so you can charge through the change with confidence
* Gain (back) clarity on your values, and 
* Align them to your career, personal goals and lifestyle to build a happier, fulfilling, amazing life.

I offer
* career and life change coaching
* personal branding support, from finding your call to making a stand out CV and cover letter
